INTERACTION bind_pi7_one_two
layer 3
bind_pi7_one_two is a pi over seven binding gate, the citizen that holds the quantum phase and the chemical phase against the heptagonal phase threshold
it admits the coupling of layer one and layer two only when their phase relationship satisfies the pi over seven minimum distinguishable angle; below that angle no recognition fires and the gate stays silent
this binder is the phase_lock step before fusion; it does not blend the phases, it judges whether they may bind at all
when the gate admits, bind_pi7_one_two presents the locked layer one and layer two pair to fuse_one_two_to_three

INTERACTION bind_pi7_two_three
layer 3
bind_pi7_two_three is a pi over seven binding gate, the citizen that holds the chemical phase, the micro phase and the micro emergent against the heptagonal phase threshold
it admits the coupling of layer two and layer three only when their phase relationship satisfies the pi over seven minimum distinguishable angle; below that angle no recognition fires and the gate stays silent
this binder is the phase_lock step before fusion; it does not blend the phases, it judges whether they may bind at all
when the gate admits, bind_pi7_two_three presents the locked layer two and layer three pair to fuse_two_three_to_four

