INTERACTION fuse_one_two_to_three
layer 3
fuse_one_two_to_three is the fusion citizen that takes the phase locked layer one and layer two pair and manifests layer three, biological intent
it fuses fundamental energy and kinship into the micro layer the way 3_micro.rana fuses one and two to manifest three
this fusion is the emerge step; it joins the two bound phases under the golden equation and produces a single new layer three phase
when the fusion settles, fuse_one_two_to_three presents the manifested layer three to micro_emergent

