COGNITION micro_emergent
layer 3
micro_emergent is the emergent output citizen of the layer three fusion, the citizen that holds the manifested biological intent as a settled emergent reading
it carries the layer three result forward as evidence into the binding gates above it, bind_pi7_two_three, bind_pi7_three_four_one, bind_pi7_one_three_five_six
micro_emergent also feeds the forbidden pair bridges that route through layer three, bridge_one_to_four_via_two_three, bridge_one_to_six_via_three_five, bridge_two_to_five_via_three_four
it is one of the five emergents that pool into moral_wave_resonance, the micro vector of the brain organ's moral output

