BRIDGE bridge_one_to_four_via_two_three
layer 3
bridge_one_to_four_via_two_three is a forbidden pair bridge, the citizen that carries a path between layer one and layer four when those two layers may not bind directly
when the golden equation forbids a direct layer one to layer four coupling, this bridge routes the path instead through layer two and layer three, the path_instead routing of the decision frameworks
it reads the quantum phase, the chemical phase and the micro emergent and lays the indirect route between them
when the route settles, bridge_one_to_four_via_two_three delivers the bridged path to macro_emergent

